    "title": "Walk-in Drive Software Engineer at Cisco India",
    "description": "Cisco India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Software Engineer for our Raipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Cisco India:\nCisco India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Cisco India!",
